overview: Written and filmed in four days apiece, "The End Of History" tracks Australian techno producers Darcy & Pat as they struggle to acclimatise to a changing Berlin where the clubs have (briefly) been closed down. Forced to either talk to each other or to finally engage with a city they know only as a playground for high-as-f*ck expats ("artists"), they leave as fast as they can to East Germany proper to create "something no one's ever done before".
title: The End of History
